entries.femaleVariant: All right. Let's roll.
My dad says there's gonna be another corp war. Liable to jump at each other's throats any day now.
Nah, there won't be another war.
I have no idea.
Won't be another war, don't worry. Arasaka's a lot weaker than they let on.
Askin' the wrong guy. Got no interest in the topic. Couldn't care less, to be honest.
Sure thing. Where to?
The cemetery.
You got it.
That was Perilous Futur for you this fine afternoon.
And speaking of perilous times, this just in – Arasaka Corp has broken off negotiations with rival Militech.
Arasaka got hit financially on that, yes it did. Still, that was nothing compared to the PR lambasting "Secure Your Soul" took. Media turned that program into a scandal smorgasbord!
Think it's true? Think there'll be another war?
Me too. They squeeze you till your eyeballs pop, but it's never enough. They gotta rip each others' spines out, too.
Know why?
Why?
'Cause I realized I don't have to.
'Cause I don't want there to be another war.
Unless my dad gets drafted and sent off to fight. That'd be OK.
Wars're gonk. They're stupid.
Whoa! I didn't know you had a gun... Hella preem. My dad used to sell ones like those.
Not without a reason.
It's a memento.
Nah. It's just a keepsake.
Don't do that anymore. Not unless somebody gives me a reason to.
Um... belonged to someone important, right?
Mhh... Important doesn't even come close.
Was a time I thought life was cheap. Meant next to nothing to me.
Thought that about my life... but especially the lives of others.
What're you gonna do with it?
Put it back where it belongs.
Anymore...?
He'd have some drill sergeant or someone above 'im – maybe bring him in line.
Can I come with?
No, wait here, OK? Won't be long.
OK.
"All possible peaceful means of resolving the conflict have been exhausted."
That's right, boys and girls. We have it from anonymous sources that Yorinobu Arasaka said today, and I quote:
I hate the corps.
You gonna shoot someone?
Now, if you've been tuning in on the regular – and I'm sure you have! – you're sure to remember that a small crew of daredemons who blasted their way through Arasaka Tower a few months back.
Got a friend who lives around here.
Where?
Can't see it from here. Just sayin'.
He a good friend of yours?
Invited me over to his house once.
His mom made lunch. Then we went an' hung out on the bridge.
I like drivin' through here. It's nice.
Know what, you're right. It is nice out here.
entries.maleVariant: You know what, you're right. It is nice out here.

entries.femaleVariant: City looks... alive.
Never been out this way?
No, I have. Just never noticed.
City slipped through my fingers. Just sped right by.
Never had time to just sit down and watch…
Nice pendant.
Looks good on you.
It's not mine.
It's a keepsake.
Not actually mine.
So whose is it?
Belonged to a woman I knew... crazy as fuck.
entries.maleVariant: Belonged to a guy I knew... crazy as fuck.

entries.femaleVariant: And now I'm here... in her place.
entries.maleVariant: And now I'm here... in his place.

entries.femaleVariant: Just a keepsake.
Oh, uh... belonged to someone important?
Yeah. Someone really important.
What're you gonna do with it?
Put it back where it belongs.
She dead?
Mhh. This piece of lead killed her.
entries.maleVariant: Mhh. This piece of lead killed him.

entries.femaleVariant: Passed under foot, over head, and I can't even say when it happened.
Um, 'cause everyone's out walkin' around?
Not what I mean.
It's like we created a monster, and never even noticed when it started to eat us alive.
Gonna write a song about it?
Maybe.
Hah. Like Frankenstein?
Frankenstein's monster, you mean.
That it is. Real nice.
The city's like a living thing.
[Put guitar in car]
You remember all that, now, don'tcha?
Ooh, corp faced some nasty accusations – psyche abduction, torture of human engrams. Most tasteless of all, though – "playing God." Ugh.
So, whadda we make of this tussle with Militech that could always turn hot? Experts're callin' it a smokescreen to take the edge off Arasaka's true troubles.
How d'ya like that? Think the Japanese kyojin can survive this bout?
[Turn off]
[Get out] Wait here.
Oh, it was just like back in Silverhand's day!
